column9: The Capital. 'Little Paris'. Palace of the Parliament (heaviest building).
Cultural Capital. Palace of Culture. Oldest University.
Black Sea port. Mamaia beach resort. Ancient Tomis.
'Little Vienna'. 1989 Revolution birthplace. European Capital of Culture 2023.
Transylvania's heart. Untold Festival. IT hub.
Medieval Saxon city. Gateway to Bran (Dracula) Castle.
European Capital of Culture 2007. Brukenthal Museum. Saxon heritage.
